snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [178] Chronicles Of Narnia: The Lion, The Witch & The Wardrobe
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: boricuaretrogamer

I am back with more longplays! And this time with game based on the movie under the same name. It was developed by Traveller Tales in 2005. It consists in 17 long levels even when you play this game in Easy difficulty it's still hard. Hope you enjoy it! -
